{
  "video_id": "qYUmI5kGsYk",
  "title": "How a video game might help us build better cities | Karoliina Korppoo",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12793.0,
      "end_time": 18336.0,
      "text": "We humans are becoming an urban species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18360.0,
      "end_time": 22136.0,
      "text": "so cities, they are our natural habitat."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22160.0,
      "end_time": 23360.0,
      "text": "That is where we live."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24720.0,
      "end_time": 28976.0,
      "text": "In 2014, over 54 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29000.0,
      "end_time": 30616.0,
      "text": "of the world population"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30640.0,
      "end_time": 32680.0,
      "text": "was living in cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34120.0,
      "end_time": 36256.0,
      "text": "and I can bet you"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36280.0,
      "end_time": 38936.0,
      "text": "that so many of these people have thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38960.0,
      "end_time": 41536.0,
      "text": "of how they would do things differently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41560.0,
      "end_time": 44216.0,
      "text": "like if I only had the tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44240.0,
      "end_time": 47616.0,
      "text": "to change things in my city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47640.0,
      "end_time": 48896.0,
      "text": "what would I do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48920.0,
      "end_time": 51520.0,
      "text": "What would my dream city be like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52360.0,
      "end_time": 53896.0,
      "text": "And these tools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53920.0,
      "end_time": 56280.0,
      "text": "this is just what we gave them."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 58120.0,
      "end_time": 60656.0,
      "text": "Two years ago, my team and I,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60680.0,
      "end_time": 62960.0,
      "text": "we released a game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62120.0,
      "end_time": 63815.0,
      "text": "\"Cities: Skylines.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63840.0,
      "end_time": 66680.0,
      "text": "It is a game about building cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67680.0,
      "end_time": 71336.0,
      "text": "So I have always been interested in cities as systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71360.0,
      "end_time": 75256.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something that I find immensely interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75280.0,
      "end_time": 77416.0,
      "text": "But what I didn&#39;t understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77440.0,
      "end_time": 79920.0,
      "text": "was that I am not alone in this."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80800.0,
      "end_time": 82336.0,
      "text": "People love cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82360.0,
      "end_time": 84240.0,
      "text": "They are interested. They have ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84880.0,
      "end_time": 87950.0,
      "text": "The game was an instant hit."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87120.0,
      "end_time": 91720.0,
      "text": "So far, over three and a half million people have played it."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93280.0,
      "end_time": 96560.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just about playing."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96800.0,
      "end_time": 100816.0,
      "text": "We also have really awesome sharing systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100840.0,
      "end_time": 103536.0,
      "text": "So people play, they create cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103560.0,
      "end_time": 106376.0,
      "text": "and then they are sharing these creations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106400.0,
      "end_time": 108440.0,
      "text": "showing off what they have made."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109400.0,
      "end_time": 112536.0,
      "text": "And what I will show you"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112560.0,
      "end_time": 114776.0,
      "text": "is some of these cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 114800.0,
      "end_time": 116119.0,
      "text": "created by the players."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116720.0,
      "end_time": 121216.0,
      "text": "So the game is about self-expression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121240.0,
      "end_time": 122496.0,
      "text": "creativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 122520.0,
      "end_time": 127136.0,
      "text": "not just overcoming the challenges posed by the simulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 127160.0,
      "end_time": 131760.0,
      "text": "It is about showing what your cities look like."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 132480.0,
      "end_time": 134576.0,
      "text": "So I have a couple of videos."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134600.0,
      "end_time": 136416.0,
      "text": "These are from YouTube."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 136440.0,
      "end_time": 140895.0,
      "text": "And these are some of the most interesting city designs I have seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140919.0,
      "end_time": 142416.0,
      "text": "So they are all different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 142440.0,
      "end_time": 144760.0,
      "text": "and I hope you like all of these."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147400.0,
      "end_time": 149376.0,
      "text": "This one is called The Netherlands."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 149400.0,
      "end_time": 150600.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s by Silvarret."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151360.0,
      "end_time": 153496.0,
      "text": "And when you start the game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 153520.0,
      "end_time": 155600.0,
      "text": "you have an empty piece of land."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 156160.0,
      "end_time": 160550.0,
      "text": "This land, it can be based on the real world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160800.0,
      "end_time": 163160.0,
      "text": "it can be hand-crafted in the map editor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163400.0,
      "end_time": 166160.0,
      "text": "or you can, of course, download a city made by someone else"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 166400.0,
      "end_time": 167576.0,
      "text": "and play in that."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 167600.0,
      "end_time": 170160.0,
      "text": "But what Silvarret has done here"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 170400.0,
      "end_time": 172616.0,
      "text": "is that what he wanted to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 172640.0,
      "end_time": 175375.0,
      "text": "was not a real city."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 175400.0,
      "end_time": 177560.0,
      "text": "This is a fantasy city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 177800.0,
      "end_time": 178776.0,
      "text": "even though it looks real."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 178800.0,
      "end_time": 183640.0,
      "text": "So what he wanted to do was a fantasy city that could be in the Netherlands."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 184320.0,
      "end_time": 186656.0,
      "text": "So he kind of investigated"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 186680.0,
      "end_time": 190696.0,
      "text": "what are the characteristics of cities in the Netherlands"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 190720.0,
      "end_time": 193296.0,
      "text": "and combined a couple of those,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 193320.0,
      "end_time": 196160.0,
      "text": "and this is what he created."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 196400.0,
      "end_time": 197696.0,
      "text": "So it is a city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 197720.0,
      "end_time": 199976.0,
      "text": "but it is not a real city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 200000.0,
      "end_time": 201256.0,
      "text": "but it could be."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 201280.0,
      "end_time": 202960.0,
      "text": "It looks just like the Netherlands."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 203560.0,
      "end_time": 206936.0,
      "text": "So the places are really densely populated."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 206960.0,
      "end_time": 211936.0,
      "text": "So what you need is highways, trains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 211960.0,
      "end_time": 216216.0,
      "text": "anything connecting these small town centers together."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 216240.0,
      "end_time": 218456.0,
      "text": "Lots of people, lots of moving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 218480.0,
      "end_time": 221600.0,
      "text": "so transportation is the key here."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 222760.0,
      "end_time": 226215.0,
      "text": "But then let&#39;s go even more on the fantasy side."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 226240.0,
      "end_time": 227880.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s go into the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 230280.0,
      "end_time": 232616.0,
      "text": "This is one of my personal favorites."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 232640.0,
      "end_time": 236359.0,
      "text": "These city designs are what I love the most."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 237000.0,
      "end_time": 240296.0,
      "text": "So this is a tiered city by Conflictnerd,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 240320.0,
      "end_time": 245480.0,
      "text": "and the basic idea is that you have concentric circle routes."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 246240.0,
      "end_time": 248536.0,
      "text": "So the city is a big circle"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 248560.0,
      "end_time": 250400.0,
      "text": "with tinier circles inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 251400.0,
      "end_time": 255656.0,
      "text": "And the thing is that you put all of the services in the center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 255680.0,
      "end_time": 259960.0,
      "text": "and then people actually live on the outer ring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 259120.0,
      "end_time": 262896.0,
      "text": "because there is less traffic, less noise, less pollution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 262920.0,
      "end_time": 264856.0,
      "text": "so that is where you want to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 264880.0,
      "end_time": 267816.0,
      "text": "But the services are still really close by."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 267840.0,
      "end_time": 269494.0,
      "text": "They are in the center."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 269519.0,
      "end_time": 272680.0,
      "text": "And this is the soul of the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 273360.0,
      "end_time": 275376.0,
      "text": "The player has to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 275400.0,
      "end_time": 277976.0,
      "text": "what are the wishes, what are the needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 278000.0,
      "end_time": 281000.0,
      "text": "of the tiny people living in the cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 281680.0,
      "end_time": 285496.0,
      "text": "So you need to know where you should put the things."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 285520.0,
      "end_time": 288560.0,
      "text": "Like, it&#39;s not enough to have a hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 288800.0,
      "end_time": 289816.0,
      "text": "It needs to be accessible."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 289840.0,
      "end_time": 291719.0,
      "text": "Citizens need to reach the hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 292960.0,
      "end_time": 297176.0,
      "text": "And this is one way to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 297200.0,
      "end_time": 301390.0,
      "text": "So maybe this is something that we might be seeing someday."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 302200.0,
      "end_time": 305800.0,
      "text": "And then even more into the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 306280.0,
      "end_time": 308239.0,
      "text": "Astergea by Yuttho."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 308840.0,
      "end_time": 312616.0,
      "text": "So Yuttho does YouTube videos and plays the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 312640.0,
      "end_time": 317296.0,
      "text": "What he did here was actually a 12-point series"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 317320.0,
      "end_time": 319480.0,
      "text": "of creating this city."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 320000.0,
      "end_time": 322536.0,
      "text": "So what he does is he plays the game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 322560.0,
      "end_time": 323816.0,
      "text": "he records it"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 323840.0,
      "end_time": 327479.0,
      "text": "and he explains as he&#39;s going what he&#39;s doing and why."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 328160.0,
      "end_time": 330296.0,
      "text": "And as a part of this series,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 330320.0,
      "end_time": 333575.0,
      "text": "he actually did an interview with an actual urban planner"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 333600.0,
      "end_time": 335400.0,
      "text": "called Jeff Speck."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 335960.0,
      "end_time": 340256.0,
      "text": "And Speck is an expert on the concept of walkability."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 340280.0,
      "end_time": 344655.0,
      "text": "The basic idea is that if you want your citizens to walk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 344680.0,
      "end_time": 346616.0,
      "text": "which is kind of beneficial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 346640.0,
      "end_time": 352376.0,
      "text": "you actually need to have walking as a reasonable means of transportation."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 352400.0,
      "end_time": 355200.0,
      "text": "It should be a good way to reach places."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 355760.0,
      "end_time": 359376.0,
      "text": "So what Yuttho did was that he explained this concept,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 359400.0,
      "end_time": 361416.0,
      "text": "he had Speck explain it, too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 361440.0,
      "end_time": 364400.0,
      "text": "and then he applied it to the city that he was building."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 365200.0,
      "end_time": 370960.0,
      "text": "So what we are seeing is Yuttho&#39;s vision of the future:"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 370120.0,
      "end_time": 374376.0,
      "text": "lots of public transportation, walkways, plazas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 374400.0,
      "end_time": 376000.0,
      "text": "connecting high-rise buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 376800.0,
      "end_time": 380376.0,
      "text": "Maybe this is what the future might look like."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 380400.0,
      "end_time": 383856.0,
      "text": "And the game system works really well for this."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 383880.0,
      "end_time": 388695.0,
      "text": "We are seeing some real-world uses to this game."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 388720.0,
      "end_time": 393416.0,
      "text": "So we know that some urban planners are using it as a sketching tool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 393440.0,
      "end_time": 397736.0,
      "text": "so while the simulation is not completely realistic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 397760.0,
      "end_time": 401695.0,
      "text": "it is realistic enough that if something works in the game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 401720.0,
      "end_time": 406616.0,
      "text": "it is highly likely that it will also work in the real world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 406640.0,
      "end_time": 408736.0,
      "text": "so that you can actually try out things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 408760.0,
      "end_time": 413736.0,
      "text": "see if this intersection might fit this kind of a situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 413760.0,
      "end_time": 417296.0,
      "text": "If we build a new road, would it help?"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 417320.0,
      "end_time": 420280.0,
      "text": "And this is what you can do with this game."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 421800.0,
      "end_time": 424176.0,
      "text": "There was one really interesting contest held"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 424200.0,
      "end_time": 426880.0,
      "text": "by the Finnish city of Hämeenlinna."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 427440.0,
      "end_time": 429656.0,
      "text": "So what they did was that they had a new area"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 429680.0,
      "end_time": 432800.0,
      "text": "that they wanted to develop in the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 432960.0,
      "end_time": 435496.0,
      "text": "They made a map with the existing city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 435520.0,
      "end_time": 438695.0,
      "text": "they left empty the area that they would want to develop"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 438720.0,
      "end_time": 441560.0,
      "text": "and shared this map."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 441800.0,
      "end_time": 444960.0,
      "text": "So anyone could download the map,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 444120.0,
      "end_time": 445736.0,
      "text": "play the game, build the area"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 445760.0,
      "end_time": 449480.0,
      "text": "and submit their creations to the city council."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 450280.0,
      "end_time": 452895.0,
      "text": "So they have not yet built anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 452920.0,
      "end_time": 456696.0,
      "text": "but it might just be that they use one of these plans"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 456720.0,
      "end_time": 459560.0,
      "text": "made with the game"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 459800.0,
      "end_time": 462120.0,
      "text": "to actually build the real city."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 464800.0,
      "end_time": 466776.0,
      "text": "And these videos that I have shown you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 466800.0,
      "end_time": 471400.0,
      "text": "these are the people who are coming up with new kinds of solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 472000.0,
      "end_time": 473856.0,
      "text": "We know that cities are growing."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 473880.0,
      "end_time": 476336.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re getting bigger as we go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 476360.0,
      "end_time": 482576.0,
      "text": "and the percentage of population living in cities is projected to rise."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 482600.0,
      "end_time": 484496.0,
      "text": "So we need the solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 484520.0,
      "end_time": 487216.0,
      "text": "and these people, playing the game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 487240.0,
      "end_time": 489896.0,
      "text": "they are trying out different kinds of solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 489920.0,
      "end_time": 493600.0,
      "text": "They might have something that is really important."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 494640.0,
      "end_time": 501440.0,
      "text": "So what we are seeing here is dream cities that might be real one day."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 502400.0,
      "end_time": 503976.0,
      "text": "So it might be"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 504000.0,
      "end_time": 506840.0,
      "text": "that this is not just a game."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 508000.0,
      "end_time": 510656.0,
      "text": "It might be a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 510680.0,
      "end_time": 512840.0,
      "text": "to decide our own fate."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 513919.0,
      "end_time": 515135.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 515159.0,
      "end_time": 518839.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}